@startuml
title LMS Backend - Core HTTP Sequence Flows

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "User" as User
participant "React Frontend" as FE
participant "HTTP Server\n(net/http mux)" as HTTP
participant "Middleware\nRecover/RequestID/Security/Auth" as MW
participant "Handlers\nAuth/API" as H
participant "Application\nUse Cases / Queries" as UC
participant "Domain\nAggregates & Services" as D
database "PostgreSQL\nRepositories" as PG
collections "MinIO\nObject Storage" as S3

== Login ==
User -> FE: Submit login/password
FE -> HTTP: POST /auth/login
HTTP -> H: AuthHandler.Login
H -> UC: AuthenticateUseCase.Execute
UC -> PG: Find account by login
PG --> UC: Account + password hash
UC -> D: PasswordComparer.Compare
D --> UC: valid credentials
UC --> H: account/person/role
H -> H: Issue HMAC bearer session
H --> FE: 200 SessionResponse + HATEOAS links
FE --> User: Store session token in sessionStorage

== Authenticated Request ==
User -> FE: Open protected screen
FE -> HTTP: GET /courses\nAuthorization: Bearer token
HTTP -> MW: Auth middleware
MW -> MW: Verify token signature and expiry
MW -> H: API.ListCourses with session claims
H -> UC: ListQuery.Execute(actor role, filters)
UC -> PG: List manageable or enrolled courses
PG --> UC: Course views
UC --> H: Query output
H --> FE: 200 envelope {data,_links}
FE --> User: Render course list

== Administrator Creates Course Version ==
User -> FE: Create course/version/block
FE -> HTTP: POST /courses
HTTP -> MW: Verify bearer token
MW -> H: API.CreateCourse
H -> UC: CreateCourseUseCase.Execute
UC -> D: Course.New(title)
D --> UC: Course aggregate
UC -> PG: Save course
PG --> UC: persisted
UC --> H: course id
H --> FE: 201 created link

FE -> HTTP: POST /courses/{id}/versions
HTTP -> MW: Verify bearer token
MW -> H: API.CreateCourseVersion
H -> UC: CreateVersionUseCase.Execute
UC -> PG: Find course
UC -> D: Version.New(title)
UC -> D: Course.AddVersionID
UC -> PG: Save version and course
H --> FE: 201 created link

FE -> HTTP: POST /course-versions/{id}/blocks
HTTP -> MW: Verify bearer token
MW -> H: API.AddCourseBlock
H -> UC: AddBlockUseCase.Execute
UC -> D: Block.New(title)
UC -> D: Version.AddBlockID
UC -> PG: Save block and version
H --> FE: 201 created link

== Quiz Attempt ==
User -> FE: Start quiz attempt
FE -> HTTP: POST /attempts
HTTP -> MW: Verify bearer token
MW -> H: API.StartAttempt
H -> UC: StartUseCase.Execute
UC -> PG: Check enrollment policy
UC -> PG: Load quiz and question sources
UC -> D: Apply quiz shuffle policy
UC -> D: Attempt.New(question snapshots)
UC -> PG: Save attempt/items
H --> FE: 201 attempt id

User -> FE: Submit answer
FE -> HTTP: PUT /attempts/{id}/answers/{questionID}
HTTP -> MW: Verify bearer token
MW -> H: API.AddAttemptAnswer
H -> D: Build typed answer value object
H -> UC: AddAnswerUseCase.Execute
UC -> PG: Load attempt
UC -> D: Attempt.AddAnswer
UC -> PG: Save attempt answer
H --> FE: 200 envelope

User -> FE: Finish attempt
FE -> HTTP: POST /attempts/{id}/finish
HTTP -> MW: Verify bearer token
MW -> H: API.FinishAttempt
H -> UC: FinishUseCase.Execute
UC -> PG: Load attempt
UC -> D: Attempt.Finish
UC -> PG: Save attempt
H --> FE: 200 envelope

== File-backed Course Content ==
User -> FE: Upload or reference content
FE -> HTTP: Course/content use case request
HTTP -> MW: Verify bearer token
MW -> H: Course API handler
H -> UC: Course command
UC -> S3: Store or validate object
UC -> PG: Persist stored object/course element
H --> FE: envelope with resource links

@enduml
